===[[Season 4]]===
Ser [[Daemon Sand]], &quot;The Bastard of Godsgrace&quot; is among the Dornish nobles that travel with Prince [[Oberyn Martell]] to [[King's Landing]] to attend the [[Purple Wedding|wedding]] of [[Joffrey Baratheon]] and [[Margaery Tyrell]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Ser Daemon later squires for Prince Oberyn during the trial by combat of [[Tyrion Lannister]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Mountain and the Viper]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
